hen I create a <span style="text-decoration: underline">reading</span> breaking point for $87E8, at the moment when is read the value is indeed 91, but right before is 00, so obviously <em>something </em>is writting data into it, right? So then, why the writing breaking point doesn't detect this change?</div>

